divs: Sighting Details I took this photo this morning of the sunrise briefly after walking out of my house I looked back ad snapped the photo. I didn't notice it at the time but after looking at the photos on the PC I found a round orb in Photo of sunrise on 12.29.11 at 8:46 am EST in Staten Island NY considering the moonrise's at 10:10 AM then sets at 9:11pm and could not have been the orb, it appears 3d round like a ball with a shadow on one side. from where I was standing when i took the photo, the object is in a SE direction. In closed is the original un altered photo from my LG-lgvx9200 3.0 megapixel cell phone camera.
Summary: orb found in Photo of sunrize on 12.29.11 at 8:46 am EST in Staten Island NY.
